ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of JOHN V. HACHEY of Baie-D'Urfé, Quebec, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Immigration at Pier 21 to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Rosanna M. Saccomani.
